result.name: 金峰靚靚粥麵

reviews.text: Good taste and reasonable price
For many of those living in Quarry Bay will be very familiar with this small local congee shop. I guess one can safely say it's one significant local eatery there.
Good taste congee, but space small, weekday morning and after 2pm is fine, but weekend morning & lunch have too many people waiting for seat & takeaways,

Really popular among locals for congee and Chong fun. This place is always busy and there is really limited seating. Congee is tasty and at a good price and a good choice for a quick bite. Better for takeaway than sit down.

Congee is nice! 炸兩 is the best! 

Crispy in every bite!

Worthy for the wait! Recommend everyone to try it!

result.name: 金峰靚靚粥麵

reviews.text: 익청빌딩 갔다가 들렸는데 최고입니다. 현지인들이 아침식사로 주로 이용하는 것 같고 소고기죽이랑 생선죽이랑 튀김같은 거 시켰는데 다 입맛에 맞네요 👍
請你的粥很美味 。炒麵更是一絕。

環境不算大食飯時間勁多人，服務好。
食物質素唔錯，粥底好靚，腸粉又好食推介🖒
午市瑤柱白粥和炒麵，粥底依舊絕佳，但味道上我喜歡早市的銀杏白粥多一回。
早上11點前，我必定吃用白果腐竹煲的白粥，lO元一碗，清熱下火，再配炸两，一流
